==Chinese==
===Noun===
[[象]][[形]] (xiàngxíng)

#one of the Six Theories ([[六書]]), the theory to compose Chinese characters: to make characters in the [[shape]] of things, like [[火]], [[山]], [[犬]], and so forth. It is the most fundamental way to make the characters. [[Hieroglyph]].

